title: natur - Wiktionary, the free dictionary
cleaned_text: gillar att vara ute i naturen He likes to be out in nature - Nya Zeeland har fin natur New Zealand has beautiful nature [nature](/wiki/nature)(essential characteristics) - Sådan var hans natur Such was his nature - ( [school](/wiki/school) [slang](/wiki/slang)) Short for [naturvetenskapsprogrammet](/wiki/naturvetenskapsprogrammet#Swedish). - Jag gick natur i gymnasiet. - I studied the natural sciences program at the gymnasium. Usage notes[ [edit](/w/index.php?title=natur&action=edit§ion=23)] - The definite form [naturen](/wiki/naturen#Swedish)(the nature) is used when referring to the natural environment generally. Compare how environment is used in English.
